            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日01:05，深證成指上漲535.93點（或4%），暫報13936.34點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-0.58%</li><li>近 1 月：-5.45%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.49%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.93%</li><li>今年以來：-0.92%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>快手概念概念領漲+7.11%。其中    藍色光標(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300058:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300058\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300058-CN</a>)            上漲        20.02%            ;        平治信息(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300571:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300571\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300571-CN</a>)            上漲        19.99%            ;        易點天下(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:301171:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/301171\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">301171-CN</a>)            上漲        14.71%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>微信小程式概念領漲+6.88%。其中    東方國信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300166:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300166\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300166-CN</a>)            上漲        13.25%            ;        證通電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002197:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https: